snippet.title: Beast Busters Second Nightmare: Attract Video
snippet.description:
Part 1 of my Beast Busters Second Nightmare capture.  I should have the full walk-through uploaded in a few days.  Ripped with a Jrok s-vid adapter.  Check neo-geo.com Hyper 64 section for info on this project.

Feel free to skip the bios loading screen.  Ends at 25 seconds.
